title: Aero Fly Pro Deluxe - True Scale
description:
New: AeroFly Professional Deluxe True Scale AddOn

Our new and revolutionary True Scale AddOn ( AddOn 3 ) for AeroFly Professional Deluxe has been released. With this AddOn you enter the fascinating world of 1:1 scale models. The True Scale AddOn features 18 new models. Besides that you will also get 5 new photo-sceneries, some of them feature our new Multi-Pano technology.
